    "name": "Homecoming",
    "steam_appid": 3013380,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013380/extras/51bdadc75d96508897c3942f54a0e314.avif?t=1755884525\" width=616 height=222 /></span><br><br>Homecoming is an indie psychological horror game developed by a single developer in Unreal Engine as a tribute to P.T.<br>The average time to complete the game is 90 minutes.<br><br>It is a horror adventure in which we must solve the mystery behind the Dewey family while various entities try to hunt us down and torment us.<br>Will you be able to survive and escape this infinite loop?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013380/extras/763f00d19e973402a5b003a32b8bc2e7.webp?t=1755884525\" width=652 height=31 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013380/extras/58dadf76ba6d31019fca29cb8c3eea40.avif?t=1755884525\" width=616 height=222 /></span><br><br>Alvin Dewey was a father and husband before tragedy struck. On July 6, 1991, the Dewey family was brutally murdered. When authorities arrived, they found the lifeless bodies of Sally Dewey and her daughter, Mila Dewey, piled in the bathtub, with what remained of their skulls dripping blood and scattered on the wall. Two shotgun blasts. They found the father with another shot in the head, hanging by his arms in the same room, but what took the agents' breath away were the satanic symbols found around him. The motives that led <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013380/extras/56606503c107214546adb7c6abd5319b.webp?t=1755884525\" width=85 height=16 /></span> to carry out such a heinous act remain unknown.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013380/extras/3d91035808f2e3f34841539844bd8731.webp?t=1755884525\" width=652 height=31 /></span><br><br>You wake up, and your life has turned into a nightmare. Everything seems normal at first, but gradually you will discover that nothing is as it seems.<br>Who are you? What are you doing there? What does that family have to do with you?<br>Seek answers to these questions as you try to find a way out of this nightmare, but are you really alone?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013380/extras/51a6de242c5a5f1f0888402cce329a17.webp?t=1755884525\" width=652 height=31 /></span><br><br>You will have to relive the story of the family over and over again, told from inside their house.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013380/extras/265b976d0c009d0e8993380944296a8c.poster.avif?t=1755884525\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013380/extras/265b976d0c009d0e8993380944296a8c.webm?t=1755884525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013380/extras/265b976d0c009d0e8993380944296a8c.mp4?t=1755884525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Investigate every location, collect items, and interact with them to survive the threats.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013380/extras/d7deff613ac07385e086f1dd8f7d1483.poster.avif?t=1755884525\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013380/extras/d7deff613ac07385e086f1dd8f7d1483.webm?t=1755884525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Immerse yourself in this terrifying and immersive experience with high-quality graphics and 3D sound.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013380/extras/37c4235ffca207285ed396c92bab2389.poster.avif?t=1755884525\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013380/extras/37c4235ffca207285ed396c92bab2389.webm?t=1755884525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013380/extras/37c4235ffca207285ed396c92bab2389.mp4?t=1755884525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
